20:["$","p","2.4. Direct-to-Wallet Execution: All transfers of Digital Assets occur exclusively and directly on the public blockchain from the Customer's unhosted or custodial wallet directly to the Merchant's designated destination address.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"2.4. Direct-to-Wallet Execution: All transfers of Digital Assets occur exclusively and directly on the public blockchain from the Customer's unhosted or custodial wallet directly to the Merchant's designated destination address."}]
