xes arising from the Merchant's transactions. The Merchant bears sole responsibility for all tax liabilities.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"3.3. Tax Indemnification: The Company shall not calculate, collect, remit, or report any sales, value-added (VAT), income, or other taxes arising from the Merchant's transactions. The Merchant bears sole responsibility for all tax liabilities."}]],null]}]]}]
22:["$","article","4. PROHIBITED CONDUCT AND ACCOUNT TERMINATION",{"className":"lend-card relative p-8 md:p-10 group hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors duration-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sm font-black text-accent/40 font-['Montserrat'] tabular-nums","children":"04"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white","children":"4. PROHIBITED CONDUCT AND ACCOUNT TERMINATION"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pl-0 md:pl-9","children":[[["$","p","4.1. Strictly Prohibited Uses: The Merchant agrees NOT to utilize the Service, checkout links, or API infrastructure to facilitate the sale, distribution, or promotion of illegal narcotics, weapons, illicit adult content, unlicensed gambling, counterfeit goods, or fraudulent investment structures.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"4.1. Strictly Prohibited Uses: The Merchant agrees NOT to utilize the Service, checkout links, or API infrastructure to facilitate the sale, distribution, or promotion of illegal narcotics, weapons, illicit adult content, unlicensed gambling, counterfeit goods, or fraudulent investment structures."}],["$","p","4.2. Termination: The Company reserves the right to suspend, restrict, or permanently terminate any Merchant account, revoke API keys, and disable webhook functionality immediately, without prior notice or liability, if we suspect a violation of Section 4.1 or determine that the Merchant's activities expose the Company to legal, regulatory, or reputational peril.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"4.2. Termination: The Company reserves the right to suspend, restrict, or permanently terminate any Merchant account, revoke API keys, and disable webhook functionality immediately, without prior notice or liability, if we suspect a violation of Section 4.1 or determine that the Merchant's activities expose the Company to legal, regulatory, or reputational peril."}]],null]}]]}]
23:["$","article","5. TECHNICAL MECHANICS AND RECONCILIATION MATCHING",{"className":"lend-card relative p-8 md:p-10 group hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors duration-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sm font-black text-accent/40 font-['Montserrat'] tabular-nums","children":"05"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white","children":"5. TECHNICAL MECHANICS AND RECONCILIATION MATCHING"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pl-0 md:pl-9","children":[[["$","p","5.1. Smart-Matching matching methods: For supported stablecoin payment options, recv may add a unique fractional suffix to the requested amount to associate an on-chain transfer with an invoice. For native TON payments, recv uses a unique payment comment. Supported matching methods may vary by network and asset and are displayed on the checkout page.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"5.1. Smart-Matching matching methods: For supported stablecoin payment options, recv may add a unique fractional suffix to the requested amount to associate an on-chain transfer with an invoice. For native TON payments, recv uses a unique payment comment. Supported matching methods may vary by network and asset and are displayed on the checkout page."}],["$","p","5.2. Waiver of Liability for User Error: The Company bears no liability for any financial loss, delayed access to digital goods, or unfulfilled invoices arising from the Customer's failure to remit the exact amount (including matching suffix) or correct memo/comment, or utilizing an incorrect or unsupported blockchain network.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"5.2. Waiver of Liability for User Error: The Company bears no liability for any financial loss, delayed access to digital goods, or unfulfilled invoices arising from the Customer's failure to remit the exact amount (including matching suffix) or correct memo/comment, or utilizing an incorrect or unsupported blockchain network."}],["$","p","5.3. Irrevocability of Transactions: The Merchant acknowledges that blockchain transactions are mathematically immutable. The Company cannot reverse, refund, or alter any on-chain transfer.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"5.3. Irrevocability of Transactions: The Merchant acknowledges that blockchain transactions are mathematically immutable. The Company cannot reverse, refund, or alter any on-chain transfer."}],["$","p","5.4. Third-Party RPC Reliance: The Service’s blockchain monitoring capabilities are wholly dependent on the stability, uptime, and accuracy of third-party Remote Procedure Call (RPC) node providers and external oracle APIs. The Company is not liable for Service degradation, delayed webhooks, or failed mempool tracking caused by external RPC outages.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"5.4. Third-Party RPC Reliance: The Service’s blockchain monitoring capabilities are wholly dependent on the stability, uptime, and accuracy of third-party Remote Procedure Call (RPC) node providers and external oracle APIs. The Company is not liable for Service degradation, delayed webhooks, or failed mempool tracking caused by external RPC outages."}]],null]}]]}]
24:["$","article","6. API, WEBHOOKS, AND INTEGRATION",{"className":"lend-card relative p-8 md:p-10 group hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors duration-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sm font-black text-accent/40 font-['Montserrat'] tabular-nums","children":"06"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white","children":"6. API, WEBHOOKS, AND INTEGRATION"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pl-0 md:pl-9","children":[[["$","p","6.1. API License: Subject to these Terms and active subscription status, the Company grants the Merchant a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to access the recv API (v1).",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"6.1. API License: Subject to these Terms and active subscription status, the Company grants the Merchant a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to access the recv API (v1)."}],["$","p","6.2. Webhook Delivery and Idempotency: Webhook notifications are delivered on an 'at-least-once' basis. The Merchant is required to implement Idempotency Safety on their servers to prevent duplicate order fulfillment.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"6.2. Webhook Delivery and Idempotency: Webhook notifications are delivered on an 'at-least-once' basis. The Merchant is required to implement Idempotency Safety on their servers to prevent duplicate order fulfillment."}],["$","p","6.3. Webhook Verification: Each webhook includes X-recv-Event, X-recv-Timestamp and X-recv-Signature headers. The signature is calculated as 'v1=' followed by HMAC-SHA256 over the exact string timestamp + '.' + raw request body. Merchant must verify the signature against the unmodified raw body, reject stale timestamps and process events idempotently.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"6.3. Webhook Verification: Each webhook includes X-recv-Event, X-recv-Timestamp and X-recv-Signature headers. The signature is calculated as 'v1=' followed by HMAC-SHA256 over the exact string timestamp + '.' + raw request body. Merchant must verify the signature against the unmodified raw body, reject stale timestamps and process events idempotently."}]],null]}]]}]
25:["$","article","7. SUBSCRIPTIONS, FEES, AND LIMITS",{"className":"lend-card relative p-8 md:p-10 group hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors duration-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sm font-black text-accent/40 font-['Montserrat'] tabular-nums","children":"07"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white","children":"7. SUBSCRIPTIONS, FEES, AND LIMITS"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pl-0 md:pl-9","children":[[["$","p","7.1. Paid Plans: Paid plans currently include Merchant, Developer and Business. Current prices, included features, quotas and billing periods are displayed at checkout and form part of this Agreement at the time of purchase.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"7.1. Paid Plans: Paid plans currently include Merchant, Developer and Business. Current prices, included features, quotas and billing periods are displayed at checkout and form part of this Agreement at the time of purchase."}],["$","p","7.2. Subscription Period: A subscription payment purchases access for the fixed period displayed at checkout, currently 30 days. Subscriptions do not automatically renew unless recv expressly introduces and the Merchant separately authorizes automatic renewal.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"7.2. Subscription Period: A subscription payment purchases access for the fixed period displayed at checkout, currently 30 days. Subscriptions do not automatically renew unless recv expressly introduces and the Merchant separately authorizes automatic renewal."}],["$","p","7.3. Limits: Plan limits may include invoice, API request, API key, webhook endpoint, retry, workspace and team-seat limits. Requests may be rejected or features restricted when an applicable limit is reached.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"7.3. Limits: Plan limits may include invoice, API request, API key, webhook endpoint, retry, workspace and team-seat limits. Requests may be rejected or features restricted when an applicable limit is reached."}]],null]}]]}]
26:["$","article","8. REFUND POLICY",{"className":"lend-card relative p-8 md:p-10 group hover:border-accent/20 transition-colors duration-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-5","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sm font-black text-accent/40 font-['Montserrat'] tabular-nums","children":"08"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white","children":"8. REFUND POLICY"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pl-0 md:pl-9","children":[[["$","p","8.1. Irreversibility: Because blockchain transfers are irreversible, subscription payments cannot be automatically reversed. Except where required by applicable law, subscription fees are non-refundable after the paid plan has been activated.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"8.1. Irreversibility: Because blockchain transfers are irreversible, subscription payments cannot be automatically reversed. Except where required by applicable law, subscription fees are non-refundable after the paid plan has been activated."}],["$","p","8.2. Approved Refunds: If recv fails to activate the purchased plan, duplicates a charge, or materially misdescribes the purchased service, the Merchant may contact support@recv.money within 14 days. Any approved refund will be sent to a verified wallet address selected through recv’s refund-verification procedure, less unavoidable blockchain network fees.",{"className":"text-white/55 leading-[1.8] mb-4 last:mb-0","children":"8.2. Approved Refunds: If recv fails to activate the purchased plan, duplicates a charge, or materially misdescribes the purchased service, the Merchant may contact support@recv.money within 14 days. Any approved refund will be sent to a verified wallet address selected through recv’s refund-verification procedure, less unavoidable blockchain network fees."}]],null]}]]}]
